	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsi ad te,<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Nr. 2328 vom 6. Januar 1546.</note> mi venerande et charissime frater, nudius tertius<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Am 7. Januar.</note> per lanios nostros simul et eas literas, quas Lętus dedit,<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3"><persName ref="person896">Frölichs</persName> Brief an Bullinger vom 25. Dezember 1545 <hi>(HBBW</hi> XV, <ref target="file12360">Nr. 2313</ref>).</note> per hos misi.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
			<div xml:id="div2" corresp="regest2">
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc nihil aliud quam vehementer gratulor <placeName ref="place70">Augustanis</placeName> meis <persName ref="person91">Hallerum</persName> nostrum<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Zur Anstellung <persName ref="person91">Johannes Hallers</persName> in <placeName ref="place70">Augsburg</placeName> s. <ref target="file12370">Nr. 2323</ref>,1f.</note>, qui ita mihi a doctrina docendique perspicuitate, a modestia, innocentia morum et singulari pietate commendatur idque ab optimis nec vulgaris iudicii hominibus<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Unter ihnen <persName ref="person17">Sixt Birck</persName> in einem Brief vom 4. Januar 1546 <hi>(<persName ref="person19">Blarer</persName> BW</hi> II 406, <ref target="file11280">Nr. 1237</ref>).</note>, ut nec vos egregii huius dati nec <placeName ref="place70">Augustanos</placeName> accepti pęnitere unquam possit.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu animos illi addes, ut quorundam odium et invidiam, quę praeclaras virtutes perpetuo ceu umbra corpus consequuntur, infracto animo et excelso spiritu perferat ac vincat, sibique abunde satis esse ducat, si optimis et dei filiis placeat, quamquam ita omnino mihi animus iuvenis comparatus videtur, ut suapte sponte absque ullius stimulis pulchre sit perrecturus.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
			<div xml:id="div3" corresp="regest3">
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tam sunt iam nostri senatus molestę occupationes, ut nondum lectum sit <persName ref="person138">Lutheri</persName>, Philippi et <persName ref="person549">Pomerani</persName> consilium<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Das Gutachten von <persName ref="person138">Martin Luther</persName>, Philipp Melanchthon, <persName ref="person549">Johannes Bugenhagen</persName>, <persName ref="person20855">Kaspar Cruciger</persName> und <persName ref="person21011">Georg Maior</persName> zur Erstreckung des Schmalkaldischen Bundes; s. <ref target="file12375">Nr. 2328</ref>, Anm. 15. Die Verlesung vor dem <placeName ref="place565">Konstanzer</placeName> Rat erfolgte erst am 11. Januar; s. <ref target="file12375">Nr. 2328</ref>, Anm. 16.</note>, de quo ad te, ubi primum, quid sit, rescivero, scribam<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7"><persName ref="person19">Blarer</persName> schrieb darüber am 27. Januar (<ref target="file12382">Nr. 2335</ref>,2-5).</note>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
			<div xml:id="div4" corresp="regest4">
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bene vale, mi charissime et optime Bullingere, cum omnibus tuis.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ora pro me nostraque ecclesia dominum, ne unquam tueri ac fovere nos cesset.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
			<div xml:id="div5" corresp="regest5">
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta fratres et amicos, cumprimis <persName ref="person14">Theodorum</persName><note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8"><persName ref="person14">Theodor Bibliander</persName>.</note>, <persName ref="person20928">Gvaltherum</persName> et <persName ref="person165">Pellicanum</persName>.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Commendo tibi diligenter Curionem<note xml:id="fn9" type="footnote" n="9"><persName ref="person20157">Konrad Hofherr</persName>.</note> et <persName ref="person21030">Mezlerum</persName><note xml:id="fn10" type="footnote" n="10"><persName ref="person21030">Jakob Metzler</persName>.</note> nostros<note xml:id="fn11" type="footnote" n="11">1545 waren <persName ref="person20157">Hofherr</persName> und <persName ref="person21030">Metzler</persName> auf Empfehlung <persName ref="person19">Blarers</persName> zum Studium nach Zürich gekommen, s. <hi>HBBW</hi> XV passim.</note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bene vale.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">9. ianuarii 1546.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutat te seque tibi commendat Zviccius<note xml:id="fn12" type="footnote" n="12"><persName ref="person264">Konrad Zwick</persName>.</note>.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus Ambr. Bl.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. Heinricho Bullingero, amico et fratri incomparabili<note xml:id="fn13" type="footnote" n="13">Dieser Brief wurde <persName ref="person91">Johannes Haller</persName> auf seiner Durchreise durch <placeName ref="place565">Konstanz</placeName> anvertraut; vgl. oben Z. 3-7 und <hi>HBBW</hi> XV 692 und Anm. 1.</note>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
